                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="15420547" author="zjffdu" created="Mon, 15 Aug 2016 01:12:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;JAVA_HOME will be set by yarn, not sure about other cluster managers. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15420747" author="srowen" created="Mon, 15 Aug 2016 09:06:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yeah, I think this is something that&apos;s up to the execution environment, and thus an issue with py4j, or YARN, or your OS or whatever. I don&apos;t see what Spark can do differently?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15420995" author="mberman" created="Mon, 15 Aug 2016 13:57:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In 0.10.3, py4j introduced an option to use the java from JAVA_HOME instead of just launching a bare &lt;tt&gt;java&lt;/tt&gt; command. So one thing PySpark could do to help with this situation would be to update to that version, and then pass &lt;tt&gt;java_path=None&lt;/tt&gt; when launching the gateway.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(change: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/bartdag/py4j/commit/189684c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/bartdag/py4j/commit/189684c&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15430341" author="apachespark" created="Mon, 22 Aug 2016 08:54:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;User &apos;srowen&apos; has created a pull request for this issue:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/14748&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/14748&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15435478" author="srowen" created="Wed, 24 Aug 2016 19:04:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Issue resolved by pull request 14748&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/14748&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/14748&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15435479" author="srowen" created="Wed, 24 Aug 2016 19:05:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Updated to 0.10.3 to enable this to pick up JAVA_HOME&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
